post_title: FS: Lajoie with Bat and Keeler Portrait (Saturday Evening Post Stamps)
post_content:
Please reach out with questions or if you’d like to see any additional photos. Of note, I haven’t yet come across this particular Saturday Evening Post Agent, “Robert Wallace Jr.” (Keeler). Also, “Wallace” is not on the list of agents noted in The Great T206 Stamp Project.

Asking SOLD for Lajoie and SOLD for Keeler. Please include $5.95 for USPS First Class 3-Day shipping.
